General:

    Mainly used to manipulate the elements on the page.
    Calculations, adding, removing elements on the page.
    Adds users interactions to the page.
    Is case sesnsitive.
    Interpreted language.
    Also knows as ECMA script which is the specification of using the language.
    Current version is ES 2020 i.e. ES 11

Variable is a named location in RAM to hold values.

    var variableName=value;
    var variableName, var1, var2 = value;

Type is changeable at runtime(dynamically or loosely typed language).
Default value is undefined.
A var can be used by directly assigining the value.
